snippet.title: unprompted – an A.I. image game
snippet.description:
Guess the words used to create A.I. images!

Unprompted is OUT NOW on Steam, with over 1500 images & AI-generated text: 
💻 https://store.steampowered.com/app/2129130/Unprompted/ 💻

Play the free web game now! Three new images, every day: 
🧠 https://unpromptedgame.com 🧠

___

Unprompted is a project by Matt Eshleman, an architect currently based in Shanghai. Unprompted is neither wholly human-made, nor wholly A.I.-generated. As such, the designer takes sole responsibility for the content of these games.

Images were generated with Craiyon.

info@unpromptedgame.com

___

Music: 
CGI Tropical Paradise Loop by dpren
https://freesound.org/people/dpren/sounds/248144/
